# ===================================================
# SmartPerfetto Configuration
# ===================================================
# Copy this file to the env file used by your run mode:
#   Local source: cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#   Docker Hub:   cp backend/.env.example .env
#
# For local source runs, if `claude` already works in this terminal, keep all
# AI credential lines commented. The Claude Agent SDK can reuse Claude Code's
# local auth/config, including Claude Code-configured third-party providers.
# Docker cannot see your host Claude Code login, so Docker runs need one
# explicit provider block below.

# ---------------------------------------------------
# AI Service Configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------
# SmartPerfetto uses the Claude Agent SDK as its AI runtime. You can use:
#
#   1. Local Claude Code setup — no env needed when `claude` already works
#   2. Direct Anthropic API — uncomment ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#   3. Claude Code-compatible provider — uncomment ONE provider block below
#   4. Custom proxy/gateway — set ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL to your proxy
#
# ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │  SmartPerfetto                                   │
# │       │ (Claude Agent SDK)                       │
# │       ▼                                          │
# │  Local Claude Code auth/config OR explicit env   │
# │       │                                          │
# │       ├── Anthropic direct                       │
# │       └── Claude Code-compatible Base URL        │
# │              DeepSeek / Qwen / GLM / Kimi / ...  │
# └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

# ===================================================
# Option 1: Local Claude Code (default for source runs)
# ===================================================
# No variables required here. Verify with:
#   claude

# ===================================================
# Option 2: Anthropic Direct
# ===================================================
# Get your API key at https://console.anthropic.com/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5

# ===================================================
# Option 3: AWS Bedrock (Bearer Token)
# ===================================================
# Use Claude via AWS Bedrock with bearer token authentication.
# CLAUDE_CODE_USE_BEDROCK=1
# ANTHROPIC_BEDROCK_BASE_URL=https://bedrock-runtime.us-east-1.amazonaws.com
# AWS_BEARER_TOKEN_BEDROCK=your_bearer_token_here

# ===================================================
# Option 4: Claude Code-compatible third-party providers
# ===================================================
# Uncomment ONE provider block. Base URLs are prefilled; replace only the key.
# SmartPerfetto uses CLAUDE_MODEL and CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL. Claude Code docs may
# call these ANTHROPIC_MODEL / ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL; do not rename them
# in SmartPerfetto env files.
#
# Auth variable:
#   - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY sends X-Api-Key.
#   - ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN sends Authorization: Bearer <token>.
# Use the variable shown in each provider's official Claude Code guide.

# ---------------------------------------------------
# GLM / Z.ai (智谱AI / ZhipuAI)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://open.bigmodel.cn/
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_zhipuai_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=glm-5.1
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=glm-4.7-flash

# ---------------------------------------------------
# DeepSeek
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://platform.deepseek.com/
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=your_deepseek_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=deepseek-v4-flash
# Note: deepseek-chat / deepseek-reasoner are legacy compatibility aliases.

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Qwen (通义千问 / Alibaba Cloud Bailian pay-as-you-go)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://dashscope.console.aliyun.com/
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/apps/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_dashscope_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=qwen3.6-plus
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=qwen3.6-flash

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Qwen Coding Plan (Alibaba Cloud Bailian, sk-sp-* keys)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://bailian.console.aliyun.com/
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/apps/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=your_bailian_coding_plan_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=qwen3.6-plus
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=qwen3.6-flash

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Kimi Code membership (月之暗面 / Moonshot AI)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://www.kimi.com/code/console
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.kimi.com/coding/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_kimi_code_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=kimi-for-coding
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=kimi-for-coding

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Kimi Platform (Moonshot AI)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://platform.moonshot.cn/
# Claude/Anthropic-compatible Base URL:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.moonshot.cn/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=your_moonshot_api_key_here
# CLAUDE_MODEL=kimi-k2.6
# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=kimi-k2.5

# ---------------------------------------------------
