# CLAUDE_LIGHT_MODEL=hunyuan-2.0-instruct-20251111

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Baidu Qianfan (百度千帆)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Console: https://console.bce.baidu.com/qianfan/
